quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  11,82,"Mana olwa likhuwa liefu lietsa, khwakhola hekulu wabu yaba hasi wabu, mana nikhubeshilia ifula yetsimbale tsieliloba eliumu."
  11,83,"Etsiarebwakhwo eshimanyisio ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, ne kano shikali ehale nende Abandu ababii tawe."
  11,84,"Ne khubandu ba Madyan, (khwaruma) omusiani wabu (ulangwa mbu) Shuaibu. Naboola mbu: “Enywe Abandu banje, laame Nyasaye. Mubula nyasaye wundi owulali Ye tawe. Ne mulaleemia eshichelo nohomba iratili tawe. Esie ebalolanga muli obulayi, ne toto esie ebaririranga eshinyasio shia inyanga ilibatererera."
  11,85,"Enywe Abandu banje! Yitsusie eshichelo nende iratili khubuleng’aafu, ne mulalemilia Abandu ebindu biabu tawe, ne mulasalasia obubii nende isasia khushialo tawe."
  11,86,"(Omwandu) okwa Nyasaye abatonyilie nikwo omulayi khwinywe, toto nimuli abasuubilanga. Ne esie shendi omulindi wenyu tawe.""
  11,87,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ewe Shuaibu! Amalaamo koko kakhulomesinjia mbu khuleshe aka bapapa befu balaamanga, nohomba khulekhe okhukhola shingala khwenya khumiandu chyefu? Toto ewe noomuholo muno, omulunjifu muno.”"
  11,88,"Yaboola mbu: “Enywe Abandu banje, mulola murie nendi nende eshimanyisio shirula khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ne yambele omukabo omulayi okhurula khuye...? Ne esie shindenya okhukhola akebakaninjia tawe. Shindenya halali okhukasia shingala enyalilwa, ne okhunyalilwa khwanje shikhwakhaba tawe halali khu bunyali bwa Nyasaye. Niye wandisichile, ne neewuwe niwenjomele."